STATE OF TEXAS
COUNTY OF BEXAR
SWORN DOCUMENT AUTHORIZING TRANSFER OF TAX LIEN
After recording, return to:
CC2 TX LLC
14800 Landmark Blvd, Suite 400
Dallas, TX 75254
Before me, the undersigned notary, on this day personally appeared BOB A STUARD, known to me to be the person(s) whose name(s) is/are
subscribed below, and being duly sworn, upon oath deposed and stated as follows:
"My name is BOB A STUARD, I am over 18 years of age and am capable of making this affidavit. The facts stated in this affidavit are within
my personal knowledge and are true and correct. I or the entity I represent owns the real property described as follows:
Account No. or Property ID No .:
11747-031-0100
Legal Description:
NCB 11747 BLK 31 LOT 10 LARKSPUR ESTATES
Street Address, if applicable:
11343 Baltic St San Antonio Texas 78213
Amount Paid for Transfer:
$6,891.06 (including taxes, penalties, interest, & collection costs)
Tax Year(s):
2021
Transferee's Name:
CC2 TX LLC
OCCC Property Tax License Lender No .:
2000067963-165504
Transferee's Street Address:
14800 Landmark Blvd, Suite 400, Dallas, TX 75254
"Pursuant to Texas Tax Code $32.06, I hereby authorize the above-named transferee or transferee's agent (the "Transferee"), to pay all taxes,
penalties, interest, and collection costs imposed by any and all local taxing units or their agents on the real property, described above, for the
tax years listed above. I further authorize and direct the tax assessor-collector(s) for said taxing units to issue a tax receipt with the collector's
seal of office or notarized signature to the Transferce and to certify that the taxes and any penalties and interest on the subject property and
collection costs have been paid by the transferee on behalf of the owner, and the tax lien on the owner's property has been transferred to the
Transferee.
"I have been given notice that if this property is my homestead and I am disabled, I may be eligible for a tax deferral under Texas Tax Code
$33.06."
Property Owner
OR Authorized
Representative
STATE OF TEXAS
COUNTY OF BEXAR
1-26.22
Date Signed
Subscribed and sworn to before me on JaniMix ( 24 ,22 by BOB A STUARD.
Rebecca M Martinez
NOTARY PUBLIC, STATE OF TEXAS
REBECCA M. MARTINEZ
Notary Public, State of Texas
